Shortcuts

SHORTCUT	DESCRIPTION	
Win Key + Enter                                           	Open New Terminal Window	            Bspwm
Win Key + q                                                 Closes Terminal Window	              Bspwm
Win Key + 1 2 3 ...                                        	Go to that Desktop	                  Bspwm
Win Key + Shift + 1 2 3...                             	    Send windows to that Desktop	        Bspwm
Ctrl + Alt + Win Key + Arrow Key                	          Windows Placing	                      Bspwm
Ctrl + Alt + Win Key + Arrow Key + Space  	                Cancel Windows Placing 	              Bspwm
Win Key + s                                                 Make that Windows Floating	          Bspwm
Win Key + t                                                 Anker window that was floating	      Bspwm
Win Key + Shift + arrow                               	    Swap terminal windows	                Bspwm
Win Key + d                                                 Open rofi	                            Rofi
Ctrl + Shift + Enter                                       	Open New Windows (Kitty)	            Kitty
Ctrl + Shift + w                                            Close one window at the time		      Kitty
Ctrl + Shift + t	                                          New Tab	                              Kitty
Ctrl + Alt + Shift + t	                                    Set Tab Name	                        Kitty
Ctrl + Shift + q	                                          Closes Tab	                          Kitty
Ctrl + Shift + .	                                          Moves Tab forward	                    Kitty
Ctrl + Shift + ,	                                          Moves Tab Backwards	                  Kitty
Ctrl + Shift + r	                                          Resize 	                              Kitty

